fll-installer (0.8.5) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Joaquim Boura ]
  * Patch for an aptosid-gnome from Angelescu Ovidiu <mrhsaacdoh@gmail.com> aka
    convbsd and William J. Henderson <tornado@tjtag.com> aka tjtag
  * changed install mountpoint from /media to /mnt. This allow us to get rid
    from the automount_popup ugliness in the install-gui. Suggested by convbsd.
  * install mountpoint moved to /fll
  * fll_iso2usb only copy the background wallpaper for grub2 when running live.

  [ Stefan Lippers-Hollmann ]
  * fix variable typo.
  * partial revert for svnr 28269:28396, as the corresponding setup code has
    already been reverted before.

