  * modules/backend/system_services.bm:
    - Replace initscript search loop by one call of dpkg. This is much faster.
    - If kelmo's python-lsbscript package is installed, use output of
      lsb_scripts -t to sort the scripts in the whitelist according to
      dependencies.
    - Remove useless whitespace removing.
    - Do not ignore previously set entries in SERVICES_WHITELIST.

