fll-installer (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Joaquim Boura ]
  * Allowing the grub's installation over a choosen MBR or over the root
    partition. No changes for USB installs.
  * Ignore install Grub on MBR of a USB device, use the old way for it.
    Accept "mbr", "partition" and "/dev/[hs}d[a-z]" as valid places for the Grub.

  [ Kel Modderman ]
  * Fix syntax error in modules/backend/install_grub.bm introduced by above
    changes (r13094).

  [ Stefan Lippers-Hollmann ]
  * Breaks: install-gui (<< 0.5)

 -- Stefan Lippers-Hollmann <s.l-h@gmx.de>  Thu, 06 Dec 2007 09:58:41 +0100

