  * We want the gdm-theme (set by desktop-defaults in live mode) on hd-
    install, only remove autologin for gdm. Fixed in fix_etc_on_HD.bm

 -- Horst Tritremmel <hjt@users.berlios.de>  Wed, 19 Sep 2007 12:59:07 +0200

