fll-installer (0.0.33) unstable; urgency=low

  * modules/backend/copy2HD.bm: don't test for /home/${USER_NAME} on target.
    Just skip rsync'ing /home if home/${DEFAULT_USER} exists on target.
  * modules/backend/fix_home_on_HD.bm:
    - NEWHOME -> INSTHOME, OLDHOME -> LIVEHOME variable distinction, with
      comments
    - don't mv LIVEHOME to INSTHOME unless the former exists, and the latter
      does not exist
    - remove fugly for $(find...); do loop, replace with a more well thought
      out find piped through a perl one liner
    - remove KDE cleanup via self-destructing script, who really cares...
    - add curly brackets around variable names for consistency

