fll-installer (0.0.19) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Joaquim Boura ]
  * wait till everything is set before umounting.
  * set right options when "de" was choosen

  [ Kel Modderman ]
  * modules/backend/copy2HD.bm: use some shell variable substitution logic to
    allow choice between rsyncing from DEFAULT_DIR or the live filesystem. For
    /dev, do just that. This ensures we have a minimal static /dev at all
    times.
  * data/exclusion_list: don't exclude /dev/*, we want to copy the static
    device nodes from the squashfs.

